  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 8eb9d9fa0ccbe1b4cbcd2a1d889b806b, type: 3}
  m_Name: FirstDayConvo03
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::Dialogue
  conversationName: FirstDayMainConversation
  lines:
  - speakerName: Randy
    line: Ah, I can't forget to mention-- check your toolbelt. You'll see that I've
      been gracious enough to lend you one of the tools you will need to harvest
      organs and materials from guests.
  - speakerName: Randy
    line: Since it's your first day, I've only given you one tool to get you started.
      It's a <b>bone saw!</b> This tool allows you to harvest <b>rib bones</b>. Try
      not to swing it around too much-- the walls are load-bearing.
  repeatLine:
    speakerName: Randy
    line: Don't you have something else better to do?
